ORIGIN DECLARATION
------------------
AXON was conceived, designed, and authored by Edison Lepiten (AIEONYX) in April 2026.
The AXON Language Specification v0.1, including its syntax design, memory
model (AI-Inferred Ownership / Manual Hint / Raw Zone), type system, AI-native
compiler features (@ai.assist, @ai.verify, @ai.optimize), and audit trail
architecture, constitutes original intellectual work protected under
international copyright law.

The concept of AI-native compilation as a first-class language feature —
specifically, deterministic AI-assisted ownership inference baked into the
compiler rather than applied as a tool alongside the language — is original
to this project as of the date of first publication.

